The Data_Reduction module reduces multiple input data elements into a single output data element by applying a specified Boolean operation (AND, OR, XOR, NAND, NOR, XNOR) across corresponding bits from all input elements. The reduction is performed bitwise, meaning each bit of the output data corresponds to the result of reducing the same bit position from all input data elements.


